<section id="experience" class="section bg-light">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">EXPERIENCE</h2>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-date">2025.04 - Present</div> <div class="timeline-content">
          <h4>現在の所属・活動</h4> <p>現在取り組んでいることや、具体的な活動内容をここに記述します。</p> </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-date">2023.04 - 2025.03</div> <div class="timeline-content">
          <h4>過去の経験・前職など</h4> <p>過去に行っていた活動や学んだことなどを記述します。</p> </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .bg-light { background-color: var(--color-light); }
  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-left: 32px;
  }
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 8px;
    top: 0;
    width: 2px;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #e2e8f0;
  }
  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .timeline-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -30px;
    top: 8px;
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .timeline-date {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .timeline-content h4 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .timeline-content p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }
</style>